item.title: Importing measurements
item.description: Importing the completed point measurement If you have not completed the AO workshop you can import the final measurement to proceed with the RE Workshop. Go to the vFunction Server Web UI Switch to the Analysis page Click MEASUREMENTS (bottom of the pane), select IMPORT MEASUREMENT and then CHOOSE FILE in the popup dialog In the Open file dialog, select C:\vFunctionLab\measurements\Analysis-Tutorial-Complete.zip and click Open Click IMPORT The initial measurement should load after a few seconds.
